  "description": {
    "zh": "好，我们继续。\n\n有几个德国那边的合作方想要他们的武器做个测试，我们就从 G36 开始。性能需要在密集林地中测试，枪上必须装有 SureFire 消音器，我估计本地的森林环境刚好合适。\n\n小心点，那里可是许多头目的活跃区。",
    "en": "Okay, moving on.\n\nA few of our german associates wanted their weapons tested, we'll start with the G36. Performance should be tested in heavily wooded areas, you need a surefire sound suppressor on the weapon, I'd guess the local forests would be the perfect place for that.\n\nBe careful around there, lots of gangs roam around there."
  },
